---
layout: base.njk
title: Услуги
description: Всички услуги в мрежа
pagination:
    data: services
    size: 1000
    alias: allServices
---

<section class="py-12 bg-primary-sand/30">
    <div class="max-w-7xl w-full mx-auto px-4 flex flex-col gap-8">
        <div class="w-full text-left">
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-primary-evergreen">Услуги</h1>
            <p class="mt-3 text-primary-deepsea max-w-3xl">Разгледайте всички услуги.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-8  pt-8">
            {% for service in allServices %}
            {% set serviceImage = service.image or (service.images and service.images[0]) %}
            <div class="home-service-card flex bg-white p-2 flex-col gap-4 w-full rounded-3xl group transition-all duration-300 shadow-md">
                {% if serviceImage %}
                    <img src="{{ serviceImage | url }}" alt="{{ service.name }}" class="w-full min-h-[200px] max-h-[200px] object-cover rounded-2xl shadow-md"/>
                {% endif %}
                <div class="flex flex-col flex-grow">
                    <h3 class="text-primary-deepsea font-bold text-lg">{{ service.name }}</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2 text-sm flex-grow">{{ service.description }}</p>
                    <div class="mt-4">
                        <a href="{{ ('/uslugi/' ~ service.slug ~ '/') | url }}" class="block w-full text-center btn-primary text-white font-semibold rounded-full py-2 hover:bg-primary-forest transition-colors">Научи повече</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


